onLineSrc.orDesc: Access to Washburn County GIS data

dataIdInfo.idAbs: This data represents municipalities for Washburn County, Wisconsin in 2019.[The municipal boundary feature class is a polygon file of all Towns, Villages and Cities within Washburn County. The data was developed using a variety of sources including, but not limited to, PLSS breakdown, surveyor records, road records, and deed descriptions.]
dataIdInfo.idPurp:
This data is intended for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data.
[This data set was developed to record all municipal boundaries within Washburn County. Up-to-date municipal boundaries help ensure the proper application of regional and local taxes, support the election process, and provide registration and adjustments for other vector layers.]
